        h3 Project definition and contract
        p Via the form embedded in the about page, tell me the maximum about your project. Android design ? Web development ? The more info you give me, the more efficient it will run. Explain me your ideas, and what will be my part of the job.</br><span class="soft">Info I might need : Aim for this project ? Target audience, planning, competition ?</span></br>Then I draw a quotation, and send it to you by mail. If you accept the estimation, please sign and return the quotation to me.
